    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini nostri Iesu Christi. XX(o) VIIII anno principatus domni
                            <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/157">Paldolfi</persName> et
                        IIII(o) anno principatus <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/167"
                            >Landolfi</persName>
                        <rs key="#sonOf">filii</rs> supradicti domni Paldolfi <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosissimis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principibus</rs>, mense Septembris, .V. X. Indictione.
                        Ideoque ego <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/330">Atenolfus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>
                        <rs key="#sonOf">filius</rs><rs key="#Personal_rank"> bone
                            recordationis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">domni</rs>
                        <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/331">Landenolfi</persName>, divina
                        inspirante clementia, compulsus de Dei omnipotentis misericordia, quam et
                        pro mercede anime meae, ut hic et apud aeternum iudicem requiem invenire
                        valeam, per hanc <rs key="#Cartula">carta</rs> offerui in <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName>, cuius domus fundata esse videtur in <rs
                            key="#Castle">castro</rs> Monte qui dicitur Casino, ubi, Deo auxiliante,
                        domnus <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/309">Aligernus</persName>
                        regimen tenere videtur, hoc est <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">integra aqua cum alveo et
                            ripis</rs> ex utraque parte de ipso <rs
                            key="#Rivers #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">fluvio qui dicitur
                            Gareliano</rs>, qui mihi est pertinentes per sigillatum <rs
                            key="#Marquis’/ducal/princely_diploma">preceptum a parte sacri
                            Palatii</rs>, habente <rs key="#Confinia">fines </rs>eadem aqua et alveo
                        et ripis ex utraque parte, ab uno capite tenet in aqua et alveo meo que mihi
                        reservabo sic derittu, primo capite quomodo intrat ipse <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >rivo</rs> in predicto fluvio qui distat inter haec <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra et terre</rs> predicti monasteri et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra mea</rs>, alio capit sic deritto quomodo
                        intrai ipse rivo qui dicitur <rs key="#Rivers">Sicco</rs>, qui est subtus
                        ipsa <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs>
                        <rs key="#Confinia #Wine">Sancti Iohannis</rs> et intrat in predicto fluvio,
                        sic dirittu per indicate fines de predicta aqua et alveo et ripis ex utraque
                        parte offerui in prefato monasterio ad possessionem prefati monasterii et
                        eius custodibus et rectoribus. Unde mihi nec ad <rs key="#Marriages">uxore
                            mea</rs>, nec ad heredes meos, nec alicui homini nullam exinde
                        reservari, sed cuncta et integra predicta aqua et alveo et ripis ex utraque
                        parte per indicate finis offerui in prefato monasterio. Si ego suprascriptus
                        Atenolfus comes aut meis heredes hanc <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">carta
                            offersionis</rs> quacumque adveniente tempore per qualecumque ingenium
                        dirrumpere aut retornare voluerimus et non compleverimus et fecerimus omnia
                        quomodo supra legitur, vel si illos de prefato monasterio subtrahere
                        voluerimus per qualecumque ingenium, <rs key="#Penalty">X(m) solidos
                            Bizanteos</rs> penam me et meos heredes in prefato monasterio et ad eius
                        custodes atque rectoribus componere obligo, et taciti et quieti exinde in
                        omnibus maneamus semper, et hanc <rs key="#Cartula #Offersio/donatio">cartam
                            offersionis</rs> qualiter continet firma permaneat imperpetuum. Et
                        taliter ego suprascriptus Atenolfus comes qualiter mihi congruum fuit pro
                        anima mea feci in supradicta ratione, et ita te <persName
                            key="#Notary #Clergy/religious_persons"><name ref="Leodelgardus"
                                >Leodelgardus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Clergy/religious_persons">clericus</rs> et <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notarius</rs> scrivere rogavi. Actu <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/571">Sessa</placeName>. Ego <persName key="#Judge"><name
                                ref="Maraldus">Maraldo</name></persName><rs key="#Judge">
                        iudex</rs>. Ego <rs key="#Witness"><name ref="Ursus">Urso</name></rs>. Ego
                            <rs key="#Witness"><name ref="Magilgardus">Magelgardo</name></rs>. </ab>
                </div>
